1. `.cursor/skills/superpowers-{version}/{skill-name}/SKILL.md`
2. `.cursor/skills/openspec-{version}/{skill-name}/SKILL.md`
3. `skills/opsx-superpowers/superpowers-{version}/{skill-name}/SKILL.md`
4. `skills/opsx-superpowers/openspec-{version}/{skill-name}/SKILL.md`

